Kiro-CLI-EULA — license summary for dev-util/kiro-cli-bin
=========================================================

*** NOTICE ***

This file is NOT an official Kiro CLI license text. It is a summary
placeholder kept in the rato-verlay repository so that Portage's
ACCEPT_LICENSE mechanism can gate the merge of dev-util/kiro-cli-bin
on a well-defined license token. The authoritative terms live in the
AWS agreements linked below, and in the LICENSE file shipped inside
the upstream kirocli tarball.

The verbatim EULA text from the tarball will replace this file in a
follow-up commit once the tarball is unpacked. That unpacking is
deliberately deferred here because the Kiro CLI tarball is roughly
265 MB and must not be downloaded as part of repository scaffolding.

